# Design & Implementation Walkthrough: "Asociación de Ampayers"

## 1. 🏗️ Core Backend Implementation (Complete)
We have successfully implemented the core Data and API layer.

### 🗂️ Database Schema ([core/models.py](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/models.py))
State-of-the-art relational model implemented with Django:
-   **User & Profiles**: Role-based system (President, Ampayer, Scorer).
-   **League Structure**: [League](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/models.py#58-77) -> [Season](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/models.py#78-90) -> [Category](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/models.py#91-104) -> [Team](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/models.py#124-139) -> [Player](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/models.py#140-158).
-   **Game Management**: Status workflow (Pending -> Assigned -> Confirmed).
-   **Scoring Engine**: Granular [Play](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/models.py#264-289) and [LineupEntry](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/models.py#247-263) models for digital scoring.
-   **Availability**: Block-based availability system for the AI.

### 🔌 REST API ([core/views.py](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/views.py) & [urls.py](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/urls.py))
Full API suite ready for Frontend/Mobile consumption:
-   **Auth**: JWT via `api/auth/login/`.
-   **Leagues**: CRUD for managing seasons and teams.
-   **Games**:
    -   `GET /api/games/`: Filterable by date, stadium, status.
    -   `POST /api/games/{id}/assign/`: Manual assignment.
    -   `POST /api/games/{id}/confirm_assignment/`: Official accepts.
-   **Players**: Roster management.

### 🖥️ Admin Interface ([core/admin.py](file:///C:/Programacion_ampayers_para_IA/ampayer_project/core/admin.py))
Professional dashboard configured with:
-   Search & Filters for all models.
-   Inline editing for Seasons and Rosters.

